ZH: 我们需要保密这个计划，直到正式发布。
EN: We need to keep this plan confidential until it's officially announced.

ZH: 请保密我的个人信息。
EN: Please keep my personal information confidential.

ZH: 公司要求员工保密公司的商业机密。
EN: The company requires employees to keep the company's trade secrets confidential.

ZH: 这是一项保密合同，双方都必须遵守。
EN: This is a confidentiality agreement that both parties must adhere to.

ZH: 在进行这项研究时，我们必须严格保密。
EN: We must maintain strict confidentiality when conducting this research.

ZH: 我们将严格保密客户的敏感信息。
EN: We will strictly maintain the confidentiality of the client's sensitive information.

ZH: 这是一个保密文件，请妥善保管。
EN: This is a confidential document, please handle with care.

ZH: 我们需要保密这个项目，以免泄露任何重要信息。
EN: We need to keep this project confidential to avoid any information leakage.

ZH: 只有经过授权的人员才能访问这份保密文件。
EN: Only authorized personnel can access this confidential document.

ZH: 我们已经签署了一份保密协议，不能随意泄露信息。
EN: We have signed a confidentiality agreement and cannot disclose information at will.

ZH: 请确认您已经阅读并同意我们的保密政策。
EN: Please confirm that you have read and agree to our confidentiality policy.

ZH: 请你对这件事保密，直到我们做出决定。
EN: Please keep this matter confidential until we make a decision.

ZH: 在谈论公司内部事务时，请一定保密。
EN: Please maintain confidentiality when discussing internal company affairs.

ZH: 他们签署了一份保密协议，不能透露关于项目的细节。
EN: They signed a confidentiality agreement and cannot disclose details about the project.

ZH: 作为医生，我知道保密病人信息的重要性。
EN: As a doctor, I understand the importance of keeping patient information confidential.

ZH: 所有员工都必须签署保密协议，保护公司的商业机密。
EN: All employees must sign a confidentiality agreement to protect the company's trade secrets.

ZH: 请你不要泄露我们的对话内容，这是保密的。
EN: Please do not disclose the content of our conversation, it is confidential.

ZH: 在进行人事调整时，我们必须保密，以免引起不必要的恐慌。
EN: We must keep confidentiality when making personnel adjustments to avoid unnecessary panic.

ZH: 请你务必保密关于这个计划的所有信息。
EN: Please be sure to keep all information about this plan confidential.

ZH: 我们承诺遵守保密协议，不泄露任何机密信息。
EN: We promise to abide by the confidentiality agreement and not disclose any confidential information.
